      "text": "急に近づいたら逃げちゃうかな？\nでも、急がないとまたどこかに行っちゃうかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "急に近づいたら逃げちゃうかな？\nでも、急がないとまたどこかに行っちゃうかも……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "speakerNameEn": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_03-cca003.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんに任せて、千紗ちゃん！\n私、うさぎさんとも仲良しだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "お姉ちゃんに任せて、千紗ちゃん！\n私、うさぎさんとも仲良しだから！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2256644089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 27.930456527
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "speakerNameEn": "ココア",
