      "text": "うさぎさ～ん、それ重くない？\n千紗ちゃんのスマホ、返してほしいな～、おいで～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "うさぎさ～ん、それ重くない？\n千紗ちゃんのスマホ、返してほしいな～、おいで～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4143426577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 48.9544685046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
