      "text": "う、うんっ！\nそ～っと……！　……取れた、取れたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "う、うんっ！\nそ～っと……！　……取れた、取れたよ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 65.9305470307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "speakerNameEn": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_03-cca007.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、やったね千紗ちゃん！　うさぎさ～ん？\nもう誰かのスマホを持ってっちゃダメだよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "えへへ、やったね千紗ちゃん！　うさぎさ～ん？\nもう誰かのスマホを持ってっちゃダメだよ～？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.441920646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 73.5925472419
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "speakerNameEn": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_03-cca008.m4a",
      "text": "ついでに、もふもふさせて――\nって、行っちゃった……残念、もふもふならず！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ついでに、もふもふさせて――\nって、行っちゃった……残念、もふもふならず！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5085873127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 82.7597135067
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、スマホは戻ってきたよ\nココアちゃん、本当にありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "でも、スマホは戻ってきたよ\nココアちゃん、本当にありがとう",
        "id": ""
