      "text": "不安で一杯だったけど\nココアちゃんが寄り添ってくれて、嬉しかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "不安で一杯だったけど\nココアちゃんが寄り添ってくれて、嬉しかったよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 101.8964479924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "speakerNameEn": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_03-cca009.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん……ありがとう！　私も嬉しいよ～～！\nこの街にいる間は、私がお姉ちゃんだからね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "千紗ちゃん……ありがとう！　私も嬉しいよ～～！\nこの街にいる間は、私がお姉ちゃんだからね！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7766548475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 110.5234484833
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
